title: Brick house 4/3 bath on acreage … bonus tiny house
posting_body: 2000 square ft Cozy 4bedroom 3 bathrooms in rural quiet area of Killeen/ 195.
House sits on 3 acres with separate parking areas for RVs and several other large vehicles.
As extra with leasing this property a tiny comple house with mini split for air, heating etc… also has a full kitchen and bathroom.
Property is completely fenced and private.. pets are welcome with deposit, livestock are also welcomed.
